name: Moth
description: $MOTH – The Lamp is the Goal. The Fire is Inevitable. Born on the blazing-fast Sonic chain, $MOTH is a memecoin that flutters toward greatness with sturdy wings and reckless ambition. Join the swarm. Embrace the chaos.
